uk.ac.gla.dcs.tp3.w.league

Class Team

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.gla.dcs.tp3.w.league.Team

  • public class Team
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a single team in a sport. The class holds the name, points, number of games played in a given league, upcoming matches, and a state saying whether or not the team has a chance of winning.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Team W

        e - Boolean to state if the team has no chance of winning the league

        t - The array of teams responsible for eliminating this team.
